<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sarvvalōkāśraya śrīviṣṇuvarddhanamahārājula pravarddha
<lb n="2" break="no"/>mānavijayarājyadivyasaṁvatsa 49 yagu śrāhi Edurēṇṭa di
<lb n="3" break="no"/>na 47 nu gaṁggagoṇḍacōḍavalanāṁṭi guddavādināṁṭi pedda
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḍākarēmi śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvaraku veliva<unclear>ḍa</unclear>vṛtti nacanaṁbha
<lb n="5" break="no"/>llivṛttiyunaina tanavṛtti śrīparāṁtakaAsalarāyaru datā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rudēvaraku niccina <unclear>grā</unclear>munaku tiruveṁṭanāṇṭi dēvaru
